Transcription.Text: "She 's as good a worker as you could wish for. She speaks our language. Mag 's One of us." Nick And his grandfather shared their bedroom amicably. The old man, though fighting a grumbling rearguard action, permitted # himself gradually to become a little cleaner and tidier.
